org.keycloak.connections.mongo.api.types

Interface Mapper<T,S>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicDBListMapper, BasicDBListToSetMapper, BasicDBObjectMapper, BasicDBObjectToMapMapper, EnumToStringMapper, ListMapper, MapMapper, MongoEntityMapper, SimpleMapper, StringToEnumMapper

    public interface Mapper<T,S>
    SPI object to convert object from application type to database type and vice versa. Shouldn't be directly used by application. Various mappers should be registered in MapperRegistry, which is main entry point to be used by application
    Author:
    Marek Posolda
